President Muhammadu Buhari has tongue lashed those spreading reports that he has been cloned, saying ” it’s real me”. Daily Trust reports that there have been speculations especially among Nigerians that President Buhari is dead and that he is being imitated by one “Jubril from Sudan”. The president broke his silence on the issue in far away Poland where he has gone to attend the 24th session of the Conference of the Parties (COP24) under the UN Framework Convention on Climate Change (UNFCCC).  Buhari: I am not cloned, I am still going strong + VIDEO It’s ignorant, irreligious  to say I’m cloned – Buhari FACT CHECKING: Has President Muhammadu Buhari died and replaced with an impostor?